file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  contact:
    email: blah@cliffano.com
    name: Cliffano Subagio
    url: http://github.com/cliffano/swaggy-jenkins
  description: Jenkins API clients generated from Swagger / Open API specification
  title: Swaggy Jenkins
  version: 1.5.1-pre.0
servers:
- url: /
paths:
  /api/json:
    get:
      description: Retrieve Jenkins details
      operationId: getJenkins
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Hudson'
          description: Successfully retrieved Jenkins details
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - remoteAccess
    head:
      description: Retrieve Jenkins headers
      operationId: headJenkins
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successfully retrieved Jenkins headers
          headers:
            x-jenkins:
              description: Jenkins version number
              explode: false
              schema:
                type: string
              style: simple
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - remoteAccess
  /computer/api/json:
    get:
      description: Retrieve computer details
      operationId: getComputer
      parameters:
      - description: Recursion depth in response model
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: depth
        required: true
        schema:
          type: integer
        style: form
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ComputerSet'
          description: Successfully retrieved computer details
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - remoteAccess
  /createItem:
    post:
      description: "Create a new job using job configuration, or copied from an existing\
        \ job"
      operationId: postCreateItem
      parameters:
      - description: Name of the new job
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: name
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: form
      - description: Existing job to copy from
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: from
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
        style: form
      - description: Set to 'copy' for copying an existing job
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: mode
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
        style: form
      - description: CSRF protection token
        explode: false
        in: header
        name: Jenkins-Crumb
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      - description: Content type header application/xml
        explode: false
        in: header
        name: Content-Type
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: string
        description: Job configuration in config.xml format
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successfully created a new job
        "400":
          content:
            '*/*':
              schema:
                type: string
          description: An error has occurred - error message is embedded inside the
            HTML response
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - remoteAccess
  /createView:
    post:
      description: Create a new view using view configuration
      operationId: postCreateView
      parameters:
      - description: Name of the new view
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: name
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: form
      - description: CSRF protection token
        explode: false
        in: header
        name: Jenkins-Crumb
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      - description: Content type header application/xml
        explode: false
        in: header
        name: Content-Type
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: string
        description: View configuration in config.xml format
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successfully created the view
        "400":
          content:
            '*/*':
              schema:
                type: string
          description: An error has occurred - error message is embedded inside the
            HTML response
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - remoteAccess
  /crumbIssuer/api/json:
    get:
      description: Retrieve CSRF protection token
      operationId: getCrumb
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/DefaultCrumbIssuer'
          description: Successfully retrieved CSRF protection token
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - base
  /job/{name}/api/json:
    get:
      description: Retrieve job details
      operationId: getJob
      parameters:
      - description: Name of the job
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: name
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/FreeStyleProject'
          description: Successfully retrieved job details
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
        "404":
          description: Job cannot be found on Jenkins instance
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - remoteAccess
  /job/{name}/build:
    post:
      description: Build a job
      operationId: postJobBuild
      parameters:
      - description: Name of the job
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: name
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      - explode: true
        in: query
        name: json
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: form
      - explode: true
        in: query
        name: token
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
        style: form
      - description: CSRF protection token
        explode: false
        in: header
        name: Jenkins-Crumb
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successfully built the job (backward compatibility for older
            versions of Jenkins)
        "201":
          description: Successfully built the job
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
        "404":
          description: Job cannot be found on Jenkins instance
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - remoteAccess
  /job/{name}/config.xml:
    get:
      description: Retrieve job configuration
      operationId: getJobConfig
      parameters:
      - description: Name of the job
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: name
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            text/xml:
              schema:
                type: string
          description: Successfully retrieved job configuration in config.xml format
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
        "404":
          description: Job cannot be found on Jenkins instance
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - remoteAccess
    post:
      description: Update job configuration
      operationId: postJobConfig
      parameters:
      - description: Name of the job
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: name
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      - description: CSRF protection token
        explode: false
        in: header
        name: Jenkins-Crumb
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: string
        description: Job configuration in config.xml format
        required: true
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successfully retrieved job configuration in config.xml format
        "400":
          content:
            '*/*':
              schema:
                type: string
          description: An error has occurred - error message is embedded inside the
            HTML response
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
        "404":
          description: Job cannot be found on Jenkins instance
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - remoteAccess
  /job/{name}/doDelete:
    post:
      description: Delete a job
      operationId: postJobDelete
      parameters:
      - description: Name of the job
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: name
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      - description: CSRF protection token
        explode: false
        in: header
        name: Jenkins-Crumb
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successfully deleted the job
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
        "404":
          description: Job cannot be found on Jenkins instance
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - remoteAccess
  /job/{name}/disable:
    post:
      description: Disable a job
      operationId: postJobDisable
      parameters:
      - description: Name of the job
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: name
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      - description: CSRF protection token
        explode: false
        in: header
        name: Jenkins-Crumb
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successfully disabled the job
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
        "404":
          description: Job cannot be found on Jenkins instance
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - remoteAccess
  /job/{name}/enable:
    post:
      description: Enable a job
      operationId: postJobEnable
      parameters:
      - description: Name of the job
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: name
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      - description: CSRF protection token
        explode: false
        in: header
        name: Jenkins-Crumb
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successfully enabled the job
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
        "404":
          description: Job cannot be found on Jenkins instance
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - remoteAccess
  /job/{name}/lastBuild/api/json:
    get:
      description: Retrieve job's last build details
      operationId: getJobLastBuild
      parameters:
      - description: Name of the job
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: name
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/FreeStyleBuild'
          description: Successfully retrieved job's last build details
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
        "404":
          description: Job cannot be found on Jenkins instance
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - remoteAccess
  /job/{name}/lastBuild/stop:
    post:
      description: Stop a job
      operationId: postJobLastBuildStop
      parameters:
      - description: Name of the job
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: name
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      - description: CSRF protection token
        explode: false
        in: header
        name: Jenkins-Crumb
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successfully stopped the job
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
        "404":
          description: Job cannot be found on Jenkins instance
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - remoteAccess
  /job/{name}/{number}/logText/progressiveText:
    get:
      description: Retrieve job's build progressive text output
      operationId: getJobProgressiveText
      parameters:
      - description: Name of the job
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: name
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      - description: Build number
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: number
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      - description: Starting point of progressive text output
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: start
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: form
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successfully retrieved job's build progressive text output
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
        "404":
          description: Job cannot be found on Jenkins instance
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - remoteAccess
  /queue/api/json:
    get:
      description: Retrieve queue details
      operationId: getQueue
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Queue'
          description: Successfully retrieved queue details
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - remoteAccess
  /queue/item/{number}/api/json:
    get:
      description: Retrieve queued item details
      operationId: getQueueItem
      parameters:
      - description: Queue number
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: number
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Queue'
          description: Successfully retrieved queued item details
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - remoteAccess
  /view/{name}/api/json:
    get:
      description: Retrieve view details
      operationId: getView
      parameters:
      - description: Name of the view
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: name
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ListView'
          description: Successfully retrieved view details
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
        "404":
          description: View cannot be found on Jenkins instance
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - remoteAccess
  /view/{name}/config.xml:
    get:
      description: Retrieve view configuration
      operationId: getViewConfig
      parameters:
      - description: Name of the view
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: name
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            text/xml:
              schema:
                type: string
          description: Successfully retrieved view configuration in config.xml format
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
        "404":
          description: View cannot be found on Jenkins instance
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - remoteAccess
    post:
      description: Update view configuration
      operationId: postViewConfig
      parameters:
      - description: Name of the view
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: name
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      - description: CSRF protection token
        explode: false
        in: header
        name: Jenkins-Crumb
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: string
        description: View configuration in config.xml format
        required: true
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successfully updated view configuration
        "400":
          content:
            '*/*':
              schema:
                type: string
          description: An error has occurred - error message is embedded inside the
            HTML response
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
        "404":
          description: View cannot be found on Jenkins instance
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - remoteAccess
  /jwt-auth/token:
    get:
      description: Retrieve JSON Web Token
      operationId: getJsonWebToken
      parameters:
      - description: "Token expiry time in minutes, default: 30 minutes"
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: expiryTimeInMins
        required: false
        schema:
          type: integer
        style: form
      - description: "Maximum token expiry time in minutes, default: 480 minutes"
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: maxExpiryTimeInMins
        required: false
        schema:
          type: integer
        style: form
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: string
          description: Successfully retrieved JWT token
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
      tags:
      - blueOcean
  /jwt-auth/jwks/{key}:
    get:
      description: Retrieve JSON Web Key
      operationId: getJsonWebKey
      parameters:
      - description: Key ID received as part of JWT header field kid
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: key
        required: true
        schema:
          type: integer
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: string
          description: Successfully retrieved JWT token
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
      tags:
      - blueOcean
  /blue/rest/classes/:
    get:
      description: Get classes details
      operationId: searchClasses
      parameters:
      - description: Query string containing an array of class names
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: q
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: form
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: string
          description: Successfully retrieved search result
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - blueOcean
  /blue/rest/classes/{class}:
    get:
      description: Get a list of class names supported by a given class
      operationId: getClasses
      parameters:
      - description: Name of the class
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: class
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: string
          description: Successfully retrieved class names
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - blueOcean
  /blue/rest/search/:
    get:
      description: Search for any resource details
      operationId: search
      parameters:
      - description: Query string
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: q
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: form
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: string
          description: Successfully retrieved search result
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - blueOcean
  /blue/rest/organizations/:
    get:
      description: Retrieve all organizations details
      operationId: getOrganisations
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Organisations'
          description: Successfully retrieved pipelines details
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - blueOcean
  /blue/rest/organizations/{organization}:
    get:
      description: Retrieve organization details
      operationId: getOrganisation
      parameters:
      - description: Name of the organization
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: organization
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Organisation'
          description: Successfully retrieved pipeline details
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
        "404":
          description: Pipeline cannot be found on Jenkins instance
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - blueOcean
  /blue/rest/organizations/{organization}/pipelines/:
    get:
      description: Retrieve all pipelines details for an organization
      operationId: getPipelines
      parameters:
      - description: Name of the organization
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: organization
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Pipelines'
          description: Successfully retrieved pipelines details
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - blueOcean
  /blue/rest/organizations/{organization}/pipelines/{pipeline}:
    get:
      description: Retrieve pipeline details for an organization
      operationId: getPipeline
      parameters:
      - description: Name of the organization
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: organization
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      - description: Name of the pipeline
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: pipeline
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Pipeline'
          description: Successfully retrieved pipeline details
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
        "404":
          description: Pipeline cannot be found on Jenkins instance
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - blueOcean
  /blue/rest/organizations/{organization}/pipelines/{pipeline}/activities:
    get:
      description: Retrieve all activities details for an organization pipeline
      operationId: getPipelineActivities
      parameters:
      - description: Name of the organization
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: organization
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      - description: Name of the pipeline
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: pipeline
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/PipelineActivities'
          description: Successfully retrieved all activities details
        "401":
          description: Authentication failed - incorrect username and/or password
        "403":
          description: Jenkins requires authentication - please set username and password
      security:
      - jenkins_auth: []
      tags:
      - blueOcean
  /blue/rest/organizations/{organization}/pipelines/{pipeline}/branches:
    get:
      description: Retrieve all branches details for an organization pipeline
      operationId: getPipelineBranches
      parameters:
      - description: Name of the organization
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: organization
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      - description: Name of the pipeline
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: pipeline
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/MultibranchPipeline'
          description: Successfully retrieved all branches details
        "401":
